\p 
\v 8 \w So|strong="H3318"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w king|strong="H5921"\w* \w got|strong="H6965"\w* \w up|strong="H6965"\w* \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w went|strong="H3318"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* sit \w at|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* town gate.\f + \fr 19:8 \ft In other words, David made himself accessible to them, rather than stay cooped up in his room.\f* Everybody \w was|strong="H3068"\w* \w told|strong="H1696"\w*: “\w Look|strong="H3068"\w*, \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w king|strong="H5921"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* sitting \w at|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* town gate.” \w They|strong="H3588"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w came|strong="H3318"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* see \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w king|strong="H5921"\w*.
\p \w In|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* meantime \w the|strong="H3605"\w* Israelites \w had|strong="H3068"\w* run \w away|strong="H3318"\w* \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w gone|strong="H3318"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w their|strong="H3605"\w* homes.
