\v 10 \w Now|strong="H6258"\w* Absalom, \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w man|strong="H3605"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* chose \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* \w our|strong="H3605"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w* \w by|strong="H5921"\w* anointing \w him|strong="H5921"\w*, \w has|strong="H1961"\w* died \w in|strong="H5921"\w* battle. \w Why|strong="H5921"\w* don't \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w do|strong="H3605"\w* \w something|strong="H3605"\w* \w and|strong="H3478"\w* invite \w King|strong="H4428"\w* David\f + \fr 19:10 \ft “David”: name supplied for clarity.\f* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w come|strong="H1961"\w* back?”
\p 
\v 11 \w King|strong="H4428"\w* David \w sent|strong="H7725"\w* \w this|strong="H6258"\w* message \w to|strong="H7725"\w* Zadok \w and|strong="H7725"\w* Abiathar, \w the|strong="H5921"\w* priests: “Tell \w the|strong="H5921"\w* elders \w of|strong="H4428"\w* Judah, ‘\w Are|strong="H4100"\w* \w you|strong="H5921"\w* \w going|strong="H7725"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w be|strong="H4191"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* last people \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w bring|strong="H7725"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w* \w back|strong="H7725"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w his|strong="H7725"\w* palace, \w since|strong="H6258"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w* \w has|strong="H4428"\w* heard \w that|strong="H4428"\w* \w all|strong="H5921"\w* \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w Israel|strong="H4421"\w* wants \w it|strong="H5921"\w*?
\v 12 \w You|strong="H3605"\w* \w are|strong="H3478"\w* \w my|strong="H3605"\w* brothers, \w my|strong="H3605"\w* \w own|strong="H1961"\w* flesh \w and|strong="H3063"\w* blood. \w Why|strong="H4100"\w* \w should|strong="H4100"\w* \w you|strong="H3605"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* last ones \w to|strong="H1696"\w* want \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w bring|strong="H7725"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w* \w back|strong="H7725"\w*?’
