\v 31 Barzillai \w the|strong="H3605"\w* Gileadite \w had|strong="H4428"\w* \w also|strong="H1571"\w* come down \w from|strong="H3947"\w* Rogelim \w to|strong="H1004"\w* help \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w* cross \w the|strong="H3605"\w* Jordan \w and|strong="H4428"\w* \w to|strong="H1004"\w* \w make|strong="H3947"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* \w way|strong="H3605"\w* onwards \w from|strong="H3947"\w* \w there|strong="H7965"\w*.
