\v 7 \w So|strong="H3318"\w* \w Joab|strong="H3097"\w*'s \w men|strong="H1368"\w*, along \w with|strong="H3389"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w Cherethites|strong="H3774"\w*, \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w Pelethites|strong="H6432"\w*,\f + \fr 20:7 \ft “The Cherethites, the Pelethites”: David's personal bodyguard.\f* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* experienced fighters, \w marched|strong="H3318"\w* \w out|strong="H3318"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w Jerusalem|strong="H3389"\w* \w to|strong="H3318"\w* \w chase|strong="H7291"\w* down \w Sheba|strong="H7652"\w*, \w son|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w Bichri|strong="H1075"\w*.
\v 8 \w While|strong="H1931"\w* \w they|strong="H1992"\w* \w were|strong="H1992"\w* \w at|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w large|strong="H1419"\w* rock \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w Gibeon|strong="H1391"\w*, \w Amasa|strong="H6021"\w* \w caught|strong="H5973"\w* \w up|strong="H5921"\w* \w with|strong="H5973"\w* \w them|strong="H1992"\w*. \w Joab|strong="H3097"\w* \w was|strong="H1931"\w* \w dressed|strong="H2296"\w* \w for|strong="H5921"\w* \w battle|strong="H6440"\w*. \w Over|strong="H5921"\w* \w his|strong="H6440"\w* \w clothes|strong="H4055"\w* \w was|strong="H1931"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w belt|strong="H2290"\w* \w around|strong="H5921"\w* \w his|strong="H6440"\w* \w waist|strong="H4975"\w* \w with|strong="H5973"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w dagger|strong="H2719"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w its|strong="H5921"\w* \w sheath|strong="H8593"\w*. \w As|strong="H3318"\w* \w he|strong="H1931"\w* \w moved|strong="H3318"\w* \w forward|strong="H6440"\w*, \w it|strong="H1931"\w* \w fell|strong="H5307"\w* \w out|strong="H3318"\w*.\f + \fr 20:8 \ft The details of what is happening here are not clear. Some think Joab had a concealed dagger which fell out, perhaps just into his tunic. Others think he intentionally dropped his sword so he would appear to be unarmed, but that he had another weapon, a dagger, still in his belt.\f*
\p 
\v 9 “\w How|strong="H7965"\w* \w are|strong="H3027"\w* \w you|strong="H3027"\w* \w doing|strong="H3027"\w*, \w my|strong="H3027"\w* brother?” \w Joab|strong="H3097"\w* asked \w Amasa|strong="H6021"\w*. \w Joab|strong="H3097"\w* \w held|strong="H3097"\w* \w Amasa|strong="H6021"\w* \w by|strong="H3027"\w* \w the|strong="H3027"\w* \w beard|strong="H2206"\w* \w with|strong="H3027"\w* \w his|strong="H3027"\w* \w right|strong="H3225"\w* \w hand|strong="H3027"\w* \w to|strong="H3027"\w* \w kiss|strong="H5401"\w* \w him|strong="H3027"\w*.
